        <p><pb n="1r"/><lb n="1r1"/><supplied reason="lost">svasti śaka-var</supplied>ṣātīta <num value="800">800</num> śravaṇa-māsa tithi trayodaśi kr̥ṣṇa-pakṣa‚ <abbr>pa</abbr>, <abbr>U</abbr>, śu, vāra‚</p> 
        <p>tatkāla dyaḥ puṭu dinulur· deni rāmanira I kapuhunan·, juru pu go<lb break="no" 
